Description: Cobra CLI demo for Debian development
 demo-cabra is a small demonstration CLI application that shows how to
 build a Go project using the github.com/spf13/cobra library
 (golang-github-spf13-cobra-dev) in a Debian/Ubuntu environment.
 .
 It provides two example subcommands:
  * greet  – print a personalised greeting with optional flags
  * version – print build and runtime version information
